{"tid":121500,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE HISTORY] 歷史科全方位攻略","createTime":"2017-02-15T09:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T10:13:24.000Z","uid":83903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc28e0db26a54b3958c942260460b5973ebae33","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:55:26.000Z","msg":"Hello同學仔大家好<br />\nHISTORY 仲有兩個月左右就考 同學仔溫成點??<br />\n<br />\n我係Johnny Sir 末代AL歷史A考生 發現DSE歷史其實同AL CE好相似 所以自2012年起推出免費資源 同時幫好多學生補習過<br />\n今日係連登分享下一d免費資源 希望幫到咁多位讀歷史既學生<br />\n<br />\n如果想拎2016年5**卷既同學仔或者join歷史科whatsapp group可以pm/ fb inbox我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFB都有其他既免費資源<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dsehistoryjohnnymahistory/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdsehistoryjohnnymahistory%2F&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=2e087370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dsehistoryjohnnymahistory/</a><br />\n<br />\n下面會簡單講講歷史科應該點溫"},{"pid":"dcc294e348fb114899b36cd9f490afdb88b07855","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:57:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1.ESSAY</span><br />\n<br />\n首先講講ESSAY既大體出題模式<br />\nQ1-Q3會出亞洲史 (themeA)<br />\nQ4-Q6會出歐洲史 (themeB)<br />\nQ7會係開放題目 (選擇課程內其中一樣野再答題 2016出左簡一個禍害 select one disaster in your history course)<br />\n<br />\n下面幅圖好general咁summarise左2012-2016既出題內容同埋2017預測<br />\n之後我會逐個topic做一個課題點評<br />\n(*注: 只作參考 鼓勵同學仔溫哂課程所有內容)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i38.photobucket.com/albums/e107/matthewma/2017ESSAY_zpswin4iw7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi38.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fe107%2Fmatthewma%2F2017ESSAY_zpswin4iw7a.jpg&h=b2548103&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38430d4f86312bbef58f81df102144df9e6a27cd","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T09:59:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1.ESSAY</span><br />\n<br />\n首先講講ESSAY既大體出題模式<br />\nQ1-Q3會出亞洲史 (themeA)<br />\nQ4-Q6會出歐洲史 (themeB)<br />\nQ7會係開放題目 (選擇課程內其中一樣野再答題 2016出左簡一個禍害 select one disaster in your history course)<br />\n<br />\n下面幅圖好general咁summarise左2012-2016既出題內容同埋2017預測<br />\n之後我會逐個topic做一個課題點評<br />\n(*注: 只作參考 鼓勵同學仔溫哂課程所有內容)<br />\n<br />\n(出埋英文版先)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i38.photobucket.com/albums/e107/matthewma/2017%20ESSAY_zpsegqnxtis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi38.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fe107%2Fmatthewma%2F2017%2520ESSAY_zpsegqnxtis.jpg&h=fd6f8af9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef5b242823299784e34cb8b9a3039a6b88568a4c","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">2. DBQ</span><br />\n<br />\nDBQ 係歐洲史 (Theme B) 同亞洲史 (Theme A) 各出兩題<br />\n而東南亞史 (Southeast Asia) 同 二次大戰後主要衝突 (major conflicts after WWII) 係唔會考DBQ<br />\n<br />\n睇返以往出題走勢 中國同兩次大戰 (Two world wars) 基本上年年有 可以預計2017會繼續<br />\n<br />\n(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 注: 2016年爆冷出左一次大戰 (WWI) 估計2017年會出返二次大戰 (WWII)<br />\n<br />\n亞洲剩返一題 估計會出日本 因為2016年其實日本係冇出過ESSAY同DBQ 加上日本同香港係隔住一年一年咁出 所以估計2017年會係中國+日本<br />\n<br />\n而歐洲剩返一題估計歐洲經濟統合 (European economic integration) 出題機會較大 除左因為自2012年出完後冇再出過之外 因為 2015同16年都出左ESSAY 估計2017年歐統會放係DBQ既機會多過ESSAY 所以估計係歐統+二戰<br />\n(*注: 只作參考 鼓勵同學仔溫哂課程所有內容)<br />\n<br />\n最後share多一個好多同學仔都唔知既技巧 就係DBQ時間分配<br />\n最簡單原則就係「乘二法則」 即係1分題目用2分鍾做 如此類推<br />\n因為題目50分 而時間係105分鍾 所以係岩岩好的!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cfdc2f6ec58da382282acfb6dd01327355bf443","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"Post一張中文DBQ出題走勢同埋題目預測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i38.photobucket.com/albums/e107/matthewma/2017%20DBQ_zpssrf1z0hi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi38.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fe107%2Fmatthewma%2F2017%2520DBQ_zpssrf1z0hi.jpg&h=35131f43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7e11af3d3d6a3b80251c0c1cd475e8f3b7bc9c4","tid":121500,"uid":85108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"我都覺得今年ESSAY香港大機會出非政治既題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終之前出左咁多次"},{"pid":"c15da08646011093742f1e3e97fe188992f30177","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都覺得今年ESSAY香港大機會出非政治既題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終之前出左咁多次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀 同埋今年香港應該唔會出DBQ 所以以往係DBQ出非政治題目既pattern都冇左 比較大機會出係ESSAY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134ab392b3478157b533f838fee0f9d98b77ccf3","tid":121500,"uid":85123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:58:56.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已inbox拎5**試卷"},{"pid":"14bef1e5642b0ac62deb7611f3a164230a940ef4","tid":121500,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:00:09.000Z","msg":"又係一條出嚟呃飯食嘅辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09205c40754483c057b69c463f594becb3798d30","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已inbox拎5**試卷</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝同學支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5cb26ea9ee52240d78765a17c09c5566d8992c","tid":121500,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T15:03:09.000Z","msg":"已inbox入gp同拎卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50253d1a9d1d4856494dff8586a76bf6c9275fc5","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已inbox入gp同拎卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該加左同學仔同埋Send左比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39f0fa766dc70f57510fc7a67f5e96edddc8e81","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>1. 香港史 (Hong Kong)</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好多學生都覺得香港好亂好難溫<br />\n其實香港出題範圍只會圍繞以下四大topic<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1.香港政治發展 (political development of HK)</strong>: 包括香港華人政治參與程度 (Political participation)﹑追溯並解釋香港政治發展 (Trace andexplain HK political development) 同埋政治發展既相對重要性 (Relative importance of shaping HK political development)<br />\n<strong>2. 香港經濟發展 (Economic development)</strong>: 暫時只係DSE practice paper出過<br />\n以往CE同AL相關題目可以係下面張圖到睇睇<br />\n<strong>3. 香港社會發展 (Social development)</strong>: 以往CE同AL相關題目可以係下面張圖到睇睇<br />\n<strong>4. 香港文化 (HK Culture)</strong>: 以往CE同AL相關題目可以係下面張圖到睇睇<br />\n<br />\n我諗同學仔都知道以往香港史經常問政治發展 (political development) (中國因素相對重要性china factor relative importance，追溯並解釋 trace and explain）<br />\n所以值得注意既係2017會唔會再出返政治發展。當然政治發展都會係香港既重點課題，但記得唔好輕視左其他方面既發展 (經濟 / 社會 / 文化) 特別係經濟!<br />\n其實dse practice paper都已經出現過香港經濟發展題目:<br />\n<br />\n而DBQ方面<br />\n睇返以往香港DBQ出題都係非政治題目<br />\n例如 2014問香港對亞洲貢獻 (包括文化 / 經濟 / 社會) (HK contribution towards Asia) 同埋2016問香港文化 (HK culture)<br />\n但係因為日本同香港多數隔一年咁出 2017年預計正路會係中國+日本<br />\n<br />\n因為DBQ未必出現香港題目<br />\n所以考評局Essay政治 DBQ非政治既出法係2017未必重覆<br />\n所以建議同學仔唔好輕視非政治部分<br />\n<br />\n下圖summarize左香港既大TOPIC同以往ESSAY題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i38.photobucket.com/albums/e107/matthewma/HK%20study%20plan%20chin_zpsddubzhkp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi38.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fe107%2Fmatthewma%2FHK%2520study%2520plan%2520chin_zpsddubzhkp.jpg&h=6352319e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e9ecd2b4645f8e2e62bf450a6302ee80941a7a7","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:49:33.000Z","msg":"出埋Hong Kong 幾大TOPIC既溫習重點同埋ESSAY既題目 (英文版)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i38.photobucket.com/albums/e107/matthewma/HK%20study%20plan%20eng_zpsef2ase5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi38.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fe107%2Fmatthewma%2FHK%2520study%2520plan%2520eng_zpsef2ase5n.png&h=9b6e704a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55ef8d48c90b2867a4b89ce819d84526209c0e23","tid":121500,"uid":85118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T10:48:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f3a6cb369d3b6d6d2e7d7b694724e54c1adcd403","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T14:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同學仔覺得邊個topic最難溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1851256b845d7a886af0eadfcdc664f42488392","tid":121500,"uid":85118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同學仔覺得邊個topic最難溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港同日本都好難記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有卷可唔可以inbox你幫手改???"},{"pid":"2fa86691e7843cfe1e328f10a7cc8acf57d664d7","tid":121500,"uid":83903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同學仔覺得邊個topic最難溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港同日本都好難記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有卷可唔可以inbox你幫手改???</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n梗係得啦!! send去我email就ok<br />\njohnnymahistory@gmail.com<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0baccddc3c2a395cee96f5e6b06423dde16175e3","tid":121500,"uid":85118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同學仔覺得邊個topic最難溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港同日本都好難記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有卷可唔可以inbox你幫手改???</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n梗係得啦!! send去我email就ok<br />\njohnnymahistory@gmail.com<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已send<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}